OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBank of England steps in   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fagain to calm markets      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Bank of England has been forced to 
OL,6, step in for a second day running to    
OL,7, boost its emergency bond-buying scheme.
OL,9,FThe emergency move came as it warned a 
OL,10,Fsell-off of government bonds was a     
OL,11,F"material risk" to financial stability.
OL,13,FThe Bank said it would buy a wider     
OL,14,Frange of bonds to help "restore orderly
OL,15,Fmarket conditions".                    
OL,17,FOn Monday, government borrowing costs  
OL,18,Frose sharply after the Bank increased  
OL,19,Fthe amount of bonds it was buying      
OL,20,Fbefore the scheme ends on Friday.      
